transfer the values of variables in templates
using pipe character : |

refer : https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.1/ref/templates/builtins/#built-in-filter-reference
Built-in filter reference

example :

{{ value|add:"2" }}
If value is 4, then the output will be 6.

{{ value|capfirst }}
If value is "django", the output will be "Django".

hello.html
*******************************************
<h1> Filters</h1>
{{first_list|length}}
<br>
{{first_list| length_is:"3"}}
